name: FATE on SUI
description: $FATE is a meme coin built on the Sui blockchain that merges AI, fortune-telling, and Web3 culture for all the Degens out there. Users interact with the FATE Bot to ask questions—about life, trading, or memes—and receive mystic or absurd answers powered by real-time data. The project offers viral engagement, gamified predictions, and integrates physical and digital experiences for deeper community connection.
